message.body: Psst! I haven't seen you in weeks now! Are you going to the baby shower on Saturday? If so, do you know when you're going to be there?
Yes were going...prob around 3. Looking fwd to seeing everyone :-)
Sweet! Yeah, I have to leave early 'cause I have another bowling tournament, but at least I'll get to see everyone for a bit. Do you mind bringing ###'s book if you're done with it?
Sure thing! I've been meaning to give it back to you
